{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"6e2e3583a8","title":"为一九六七年七月三十日《人民日报》社论加的一句话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"4c27ff0fa7","index":0,"year":1967,"month":7,"day":null,"articleId":"6e2e3583a8"}],"tags":[{"id":"0d8f653275","name":"武汉地区无产阶级革命派百万雄师联络站（百万雄师）","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","name":"毛泽东思想万岁（1961年-1968年）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives3/main/45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"3a760a8434","type":"paragraph","text":"四、要向左派作工作，不要乘机报复五、要馨惕坏人揭乱，不许破坏社会秩序。","index":0,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"6e2e3583a8"},{"id":"c0228b9028","type":"paragraph","text":"对武汉事件的指示","index":1,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"6e2e3583a8"},{"id":"cd63f3e4b4","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六七年七月）本来军内的问题没有机会解决，武汉问题发生了，就有机会解决了，机会是他们给的。","index":2,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"6e2e3583a8"},{"id":"810a52c55d","type":"paragraph","text":"XX","index":3,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"6e2e3583a8"},{"id":"688c50cbd8","type":"paragraph","text":"X","index":4,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"6e2e3583a8"},{"id":"c8f5df76ac","type":"paragraph","text":"全国都应该从武汉事件中学习。全国支持武汉地区，武汉地区的斗争推动了全国的工作。一年来发生了天翻地复的变化，当然有点乱。这里乱那里也乱，没有什么关系。象武汉这是很好的事，矛盾暴露了就好解决。","index":5,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"6e2e3583a8"},{"id":"38d9420d21","type":"paragraph","text":"武汉一小搬人的频变行为可以使全国的解放军、革命造反派、群众组织从中得到教育这次文化大革命损失是最小最小最小的，成绩是最大最大最大的。","index":6,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"6e2e3583a8"},{"id":"78ad3caa4b","type":"paragraph","text":"X十","index":7,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"6e2e3583a8"},{"id":"b469741ffe","type":"paragraph","text":"X对“百万雄师”一个也不抓，几个坏头头让他们自己检举。","index":8,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"6e2e3583a8"},{"id":"37a01dc7a9","type":"paragraph","text":"关于“八一”建军节的指示","index":9,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"6e2e3583a8"},{"id":"13180bb7a5","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六七年七月）","index":10,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"6e2e3583a8"},{"id":"02b09ee88f","type":"paragraph","text":"“八一”不能改，这是很重要的一天。我们打响了第一枪，为井岗山的斗争揭开了序幕。","index":11,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"6e2e3583a8"},{"id":"970bfd8b2e","type":"paragraph","text":"这个问题是历史问题，历史问题是不容题倒的。","index":12,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"6e2e3583a8"},{"id":"ff1955f91a","type":"paragraph","text":"为一九六七年七月开日《人民日报》","index":13,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"6e2e3583a8"},{"id":"065ca07b76","type":"paragraph","text":"社加的一句斋","index":14,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"6e2e3583a8"},{"id":"4633d4f999","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六七年七月）团结一致，同心同德，任何强大的敌人，任何困难的坏境，都会向我们投降的。","index":15,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"6e2e3583a8"},{"id":"c80396ac61","type":"paragraph","text":"321","index":16,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"6e2e3583a8"}],"page":{"id":"e68f7a9e00","publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"6e2e3583a8","start":334,"end":334}}}},"__N_SSG":true}